title: U.S. Cado Holdings, Inc. Recalls Imported Siluriformes Fish Products Distributed Without Meeting Fsis Requirements
summary: EDITORS NOTE: This release is being reissued as an expansion of the June 20, 2016 and June 25, 2016 recalls to include additional products, production dates, and distribution area. The first recall 052-2016 on June 20, 2016 involved 25,760 pounds of frozen swai fillet products...
